content.rendered:
Maharashtra Leadership Awards 2022
Shri Sangram Kamble
Shri Nilesh Pasalkar
Shri Savan Oswal
partners, Kiosk Kaffee
For their contribution to the Indian Coffee Industry
felicitated by
Honorable Governer of Maharashtra
shri Bhagat Singh Koshyari.
